'''Chaeldar''' is the fourth most-advanced [[slayer master]] in ''[[Old School RuneScape|RuneScape]]''. She is found in the throne room of [[Zanaris]], directly south of the entrance from the [[Lumbridge Swamp]], meaning completion of the [[Lost City]] [[quest]] is required to reach her. She gives out mid to high level [[Slayer]] [[Slayer task|tasks]], which may only be attempted by players with a [[combat level]] of at least 70.

Unlike [[Mazchna]] and [[Vannaka]] none of her tasks require the player to kill Wilderness-only monsters (such as [[Earth warrior]]s).

Getting a slayer task from Chaeldar is a task in the [[Lumbridge & Draynor Medium Diary]].

